text: Vilmos Göttler (born 22 December 1951) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Békéscsaba
